**Account Deletion Request**

If you would like to delete your account and associated data, please follow the steps below:

1. Send a request to our support email: [tranhaidong060916@gmail.com](mailto:tranhaidong060916@gmail.com)
2. Include your account email address used in the app
3. We will process your request within 3-5 business days

**Data Deletion**

When your account is deleted:

* Your email and account information will be permanently deleted
* Your learning progress and activity data will be removed

Some data may be retained temporarily for legal or security purposes.

If you have any questions, please contact: [tranhaidong060916@gmail.com](mailto:tranhaidong060916@gmail.com)
